@node Future "Future"
Future versions of GBlist will hopefully do/have the following:

 - Check ROM/RAM requirements of carts.
 - Proper wildcards support.
 - Exclusion of any files which aren't gameboy carts.

Any other suggestions? Mail @{"me" LINK Credits}!
@endnode
